w.nme.com/news/music/manchester-co-op-live-arena-boss-resigns-after-rows-controversy-and-venue-problems-3750847">随后竞技场老板加里·罗登 (Gary Roden) 很快辞职</a>。</p><p>其他受到这些问题影响的音乐会包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/and-now-co-op-live-have-postponed-olivia-rodrigos-gigs-too-3752542">Olivia Rodrigo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-co-op-live-arena-sees-further-problems-and-delays-as-the-black-keys-and-peter-kay-forced-to-postpone-shows-3751134">The Black Keys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keane-cancel-manchester-show-take-that-move-to-ao-arena-due-to-co-op-live-chaos-3752973">Take That</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-co-op-live-arena-pulls-a-boogie-wit-da-hoodie-show-last-minute-due-to-venue-related-technical-issue-3752508">A Boogie Wit Da Hoodie</a>的音乐会。</p><p>后者的活动在最后一刻被取消，原因是“与场地相关的技术问题”——后来证实是空调机组的一部分从天花板上掉下来（来自<a href="https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/whats-on/whats-on-news/co-op-lives-first-show-29096609" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《曼彻斯特晚报</em></a>》）。没有人受伤。</p><p>在 5 月 2 日的一份声明中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/co-op-live-reveal-new-opening-date-and-apologise-its-not-been-the-smooth-start-we-had-planned-for-3752992">Co-Op Live 宣布新的开业日期为 5 月 14 日</a>，并表示团队“正在非常努力地进行建设和运行”。上周，该场馆在接受《 <a href="https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/whats-on/music-nightlife-news/co-op-live-bosses-say-29133990" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>曼彻斯特晚报》</em></a>采访时解释道： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-co-op-live-expecting-elbow-opening-gig-to-go-ahead-after-spate-of-delays-3755349">“目前，我们预计不会对我们的开幕赛季产生进一步影响。”</a></p><p>据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cg399l719jjo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司新闻</em></a>报道，Co-Op Live现已通过最终检查，终于可以开业了。</p><p>昨天（5 月 13 日），Elbow 分享了一张他们在会场舞台上搭建的装备的图片，这表明一切进展顺利且准时。 “为明天的 Co-Op Live 竞技场做好准备。再见。”乐队为照片加上了标题。见下文。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C66ex