/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/manchester_co_op-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3753533" class="wp-caption-text">曼彻斯特的 Co-Op Live 竞技场。图片来源：Peter Byrne/PA Images/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>在辞职之前，加里·罗登（Gary Roden）驳回了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-case-has-been-made-for-a-1-ticket-levy-on-all-arena-gigs-for-the-survival-of-grassroots-venues-and-artists-3611533">对所有大型及以上演出场地征收门票的呼吁</a>，这一建议是为了确保英国各地小型场馆的未来。他还因称一些基层场馆“经营不善”而引发争议。</p><p>作为回应， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-say-manchester-co-op-live-arena-comments-were-disrespectful-and-disingenuous-and-call-on-1-ticket-levy-to-save-uk-talent-pipeline-3749732">MVT 首席执行官马克·戴维德 (Mark Davyd) 告诉<em>《NME》</em> ，他认为罗登的言论“不尊重且不诚实”</a> 。他指出，本周 Co-Op Live Arena 因众多后勤问题而被迫推迟推出，而发表此类<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-hit-back-at-manchesters-co-op-live-for-saying-some-grassroots-venues-are-poorly-run-despite-arena-facing-own-major-issues-3749643">“判断失误、不必要和误导性”的评论</a>具有讽刺意味。</p><p>戴维德表示，新竞技场最初“拒绝了适当参与有关英国现场音乐生态系统未来讨论的邀请”。</p><p>其他计划在曼彻斯特 Co-Op Live 演出的乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-keys">The Black Keys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">Eric Clapton</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eagles">Eagles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pet-shop-boys">Pet Shop Boys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elbow-are-ready-to-open-manchesters-co-op-live-arena-tonight-after-weeks-of-chaos-see-you-there-3755979">经过数周的混乱之后，Post Elbow 已“准备好”今晚在曼彻斯特的 Co-Op Live 竞技场开幕：《那儿见》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
警方称荷兰被取消欧洲歌唱大赛资格的选手乔斯特·克莱因可能面临指控https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-netherlands-disqualified-eurovision-contestant-joost-klein-likely-to-face-charges-say-police-3756003?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-荷兰被取消欧洲电视网参赛资格的选手约斯特·克莱因可能面临警察指控Liberty DunworthTue, 14 May 2024 09:45:20 +0000 Music NewsNews..Eurovision https://www.nme.com/?p=3756003 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="荷兰歌手 Joost Klein 代表荷兰参加 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在被指控对制作人员进行口头威胁后，他被排除在大结局之外</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-netherlands-disqualified-eurovision-contestant-joost-klein-likely-to-face-charges-say-police-3756003">荷兰被取消欧洲歌唱大赛资格的选手 Joost Klein 可能面临指控，称警方</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="荷兰歌手 Joost Klein 代表荷兰参加 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-Eurovision@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据警方称，被取消<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/eurovision">欧洲歌唱大赛</a>资格的荷兰选手可能会面临指控。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/eurovision-boycotts-protest-fans-watching-2024-israel-palestine-3755156">在观看 2024 年欧洲电视网的激烈辩论中：“这感觉比比赛更重要”</a></strong></li></ul><p> Joost Klein 原本准备代表荷兰演唱歌曲《Europapa》， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-netherlands-eurovision-entry-joost-klein-kicked-out-of-competition-3755424">但在周六决赛（5 月 11 日）前几个小时，他被取消了在瑞典马尔默举行的比赛的资格</a>。当时，警方表示，这一决定是在他被指控对剧组一名女性成员进行口头威胁后做出的。</p><p>此次事件标志着该比赛68年历史上首次出现进入总决赛后被取消资格的行为，而在被取消资格之前，这位26岁的歌手被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/who-will-win-eurovision-2024-here-are-the-latest-bookies-odds-3750332">评为最有希望获胜的歌手之一</a>。</p><p>现在，警方发言人吉米·莫丁（Jimmy Modin）向<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/article/2024/may/14/disqualified-eurovision-contestant-joost-klein-likely-to-face-charges-say-swedish-police" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>讲述了这起不雅事件，并透露克莱因很可能将面临法律诉讼。</p><p>莫丁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/netherlands-eurovision-entry-joost-klein-being-investigated-and-not-rehearsing-until-further-notice-over-incident-3755320">证实，调查已经结束</a>，“未来几周内”将做出是否提出指控的决定。</p><p>负责此案的警官埃米尔·安德森 (Emil Andersson) 与瑞典广播公司 SVT 也有类似的看法。他说：“我们预计可能会提起诉讼。”他还补充说，由于争吵并未涉及更严重的犯罪，因此可能会“加速起诉”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756015" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756015" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756015" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-performs@2000x1270.jpg" alt="荷兰歌手 Joost Klein 代表荷兰参加 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-performs@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-performs@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-performs@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-performs@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-performs@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein-performs@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756015" class="wp-caption-text">荷兰歌手 Joost Klein 代表荷兰参加 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛。图片来源：Tobias SCHWARZ / AFP / Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>有关所指控威胁的性质的更多细节尚未公开披露。</p><p>在他被取消资格的消息传出后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dutch-broadcaster-says-they-are-very-disappointed-and-upset-over-eurovision-entry-joost-kleins-disqualification-3755459">荷兰广播公司 Avrotros 表示对这一决定感到“震惊”</a> ，并表示虽然克莱因对一名女摄影师做出了“威胁性举动”，但他并没有碰她（来自<em>《卫报》）</em> 。</p><p> “违反了明确的约定，乔斯特在他刚刚下台并不得不赶往演员休息室时就被拍摄了。当时，乔斯特一再表示他不想被拍摄。这没有得到尊重，”Avrotros 补充道。</p><p>此后克莱因尚未对这一事件发表公开评论。</p><p> EBU 更新了他已退出歌曲比赛的消息。声明全文如下：“荷兰艺术家 Joost Klein 将不会参加今年欧洲歌唱大赛的总决赛。</p><p> “瑞典警方已调查一名女制作人员在周四晚的半决赛表演后发生的事件后提出的投诉。虽然法律程序正在顺利进行，但他继续参加比赛并不合适。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756016" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756016" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756016" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein@2000x1270.jpg" alt="荷兰歌手 Joost Klein 代表荷兰参加 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Joost-Klein@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756016" class="wp-caption-text">荷兰歌手 Joost Klein 代表荷兰参加 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛。图片来源：Ida Marie Odgaard / Ritzau Scanpix / AFP/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “我们想澄清的是，与一些媒体报道和社交媒体猜测相反，这一事件并未涉及任何其他表演者或代表团成员。</p><p> “我们对活动中的不当行为采取零容忍政策，并致力于为比赛的所有工作人员提供一个安全可靠的工作环境。有鉴于此，Joost Klein 对团队成员的行为被视为违反了比赛规则。”</p><p>今年的比赛<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/switzerlands-nemo-wins-eurovision-song-contest-2024-3755482">最终由瑞士选手尼莫获胜</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/eurovision-boycotts-protest-fans-watching-2024-israel-palestine-3755156">但由于允许以色列在加沙与哈马斯持续冲突的情况下参加比赛，引发了争议</a>。</p><p>自决赛以来，它还面临欧盟委员会副主席玛加里蒂斯希纳斯的批评，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eu-accuses-eurovision-bosses-of-handing-win-to-enemies-of-europe-with-flag-ban-3755735">指责比赛老板通过禁止欧盟旗帜的决定将“胜利”拱手让给“欧洲的敌人”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-netherlands-disqualified-eurovision-contestant-joost-klein-likely-to-face-charges-say-police-3756003">荷兰被取消欧洲歌唱大赛资格的选手 Joost Klein 可能面临指控，称警方</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《小驯鹿》的创作者理查德·加德 (Richard Gadd) 讲述了他最喜欢的乐队 The Pogues 是如何激励他的https://www.nme.com/news/tv/baby-reindeer-creator-richard-gadd-the-pogues-inspired-him-3755983?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=baby-reindeer-creator-richard-gadd-波格斯启发了他Elizabeth AubreyTue, 14 May 2024 09:33:55 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3755983 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="理查德·加德和肖恩·麦高恩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他们给了我很大的启发”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/baby-reindeer-creator-richard-gadd-the-pogues-inspired-him-3755983">《Baby Reindeer》帖子的创作者 Richard Gadd 讲述了他最喜欢的乐队 The Pogues 如何激励他</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="理查德·加德和肖恩·麦高恩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Richard-gadd-Shane-MacG-and-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/baby-reindeer"><i>《小驯鹿》</i></a>的创作者理查德·加德 (Richard Gadd) 讲述了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shane-macgowan">肖恩·麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pogues">波格斯乐队 (The Pogues)</a>对他的作品的影响。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/shane-macgowan-obituary-the-pogues-3551303">Shane MacGowan，1957-2023：一位毫不妥协的独一无二的人</a></strong></li></ul><p>加德最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">在 Netflix 上</a>播出的剧集声称讲述了他现实生活中的跟踪经历的“真实故事”，并在网上疯传后登上了流媒体排行榜的榜首。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-features/richard-gadd-baby-reindeer-fame-real-people-1235897317/amp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《好莱坞报道》的</i></a>一次新采访中，加德谈到了他的灵感，特别是波格斯乐队和已故肖恩·麦高恩的音乐。</p><p>这位爱尔兰音乐家兼标志性主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pogues-shane-macgowan-has-died-aged-65-3551301">于 11 月 30 日因肺炎在医院“平静”去世</a>。他今年 65 岁。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glen-hansard-and-lisa-oneill-perform-fairytale-of-new-york-at-shane-macgowans-funeral-3556366">他的葬礼于 12 月 8 日在蒂珀雷里郡尼纳举行</a>。</p><p>去年12月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-line-the-streets-of-dublin-for-shane-macgowan-funeral-3556189">，麦高恩的葬礼在爱尔兰蒂珀雷里郡尼纳举行，粉丝们聚集在都柏林街道两旁，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/johnny-depp-salutes-maestro-shane-macgowan-during-funeral-reading-3556302">出席葬礼的有</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glen-hansard-and-lisa-oneill-perform-fairytale-of-new-york-at-shane-macgowans-funeral-3556366">格伦·汉萨德</a>和爱尔兰总统迈克尔·D·希金斯。</p><p>谈到 MacGowan 以及乐队对他的影响，Gadd 解释道：“Shane 和 Pogues 产生了巨大的影响。我遇到了一个人……他的男朋友是这个节目的制作人，所以他们给了我一张后台通行证。我当时想，‘你在开玩笑吗？我要去见波格斯夫妇？我遇到了来自 Pogues 的[Spider Stacy、Jem Finer 和 James Fearnley]，他们都看过这个节目。</p><p> “我简直不敢相信。我发帖说我见到了波格斯夫妇，然后他们真的把它发布到了他们的官方 Instagram 上，这是他们和我的合影，这真是令人难以置信。他们给了我很大的启发。”</p><p>您可以在这里查看该帖子： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/B5CuZxyHXJa/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,