ar-announce-new-album-the-greatest-love-with-hypnotic-lead-single-house-3613735">《The Greatest Love</a> 》之前带着单曲《House》回归，计划于 5 月 26 日星期日在 Radio 1 主舞台上演出，AJ Tracey 也是如此。</p><p>请参阅下面完整的修订后的阵容，并<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/events/eqdmzc/performances#all" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处查找更多信息</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BigWeekend?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#BigWeekend</a>卢顿阵容中添加了新名字<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2728.png" alt="✨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ajtracey?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@ajtracey</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/JaxJones?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@JaxJones</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/londongrammar?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@londongrammar</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/NathanDawe?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@NathanDawe</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/remiwolf?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@remiwolf</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/WilkinsonUK?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@WilkinsonUK</a></p><p>通过<a href="https://twitter.com/BBCiPlayer?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@BBCiPlayer</a>观看音乐节现场直播或通过<a href="https://twitter.com/BBCSounds?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@BBCSounds</a>收听。 <a href="https://t.co/ZIujk9VMSu">pic.twitter.com/ZIujk9VMSu</a></p><p> — BBC 广播 1 台 (@BBCR1) <a href="https://twitter.com/BBCR1/status/1790282657114296408?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>其他上榜艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/becky-hill">Becky Hill</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/everything-everything">Everything Everything</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean">Olivia Dean</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beabadoobee">