安雅·泰勒-乔伊在《Furiosa》中只有 30 句台词，连续“几个月”没有在片场发言https://www.nme.com/news/film/anya-taylor-joy-only-has-30-lines-of-dialogue-in-furiosa-went-months-without-speaking-on-set-3755963？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=anya-taylor-joy-only-has-30-lines-of-Dialogue-in-furiosa-goed-months-without-speaking-on-setSurej Singh Tue, 14 May 2024 08:20:27 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3755963 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据导演乔治·米勒的说法，对话“往往会放慢速度，而电影是一种通常最好在高速下欣赏的媒介”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anya-taylor-joy-only-has-30-lines-of-dialogue-in-furiosa-went-months-without-speaking-on-set-3755963">安雅·泰勒-乔伊 (Anya Taylor-Joy) 在《Furiosa》中只有 30 句台词，“几个月”没有在片场讲话的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/anya-taylor-joy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/furiosa"><em>《福瑞奥莎</em></a>》的主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anya-taylor-joy">安雅·泰勒-乔伊</a>不会在即将上映的电影中发表太多言论 - 请在下文中了解原因。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="5"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-16075-315225"><b>《疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路》——电影评论</b></a></li></ul><p>在最近接受<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/2024/05/11/tom-hardy-george-miller-mad-max-furiosa-interview/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《电讯报》</em></a>采访时，导演乔治·米勒透露，饰演福瑞奥莎的泰勒-乔伊在整部电影中只有“大约”30 行对白。</p><p> <em>《疯狂的麦克斯》</em>系列中的所有主演在他们的电影中都没有太多对话；<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mel-gibson">梅尔·吉布森</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-hardy">汤姆·哈迪</a>在各自的电影中都很少说话。米勒解释说，对话往往会减慢速度，而电影是一种最适合高速观看的媒介。相反，米勒依靠主演的面部反应和举止来讲述故事。 </p><figure id="attachment_3754045" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3754045" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3754045" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa.jpg" alt="福里奥萨" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Mad-Max-Furiosa-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3754045" class="wp-caption-text">安雅·泰勒-乔伊在《福瑞奥萨：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》中。图片来源：Jasin Boland/华纳兄弟</figcaption></figure><p>安雅·泰勒-乔伊在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/05/12/movies/anya-taylor-joy-furiosa.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时透露，台词数量极其有限，这意味着她“几个月”没有说过或录制一行对话。</p><p>然而，她表示，为了加入米勒最初反对的尖叫声，她“奋斗了三个月”。在解释米勒的方法时，泰勒-乔伊说：“他对福瑞奥莎的战争面孔有一个非常非常严格的想法，这只让我能够看到电影的大部分内容。这就是“闭嘴​​，没有情感，用眼睛说话”。就是这样，这就是你所拥有的一切。”</p><p>她继续说道：“我是女性愤怒的坚定倡导者。我们都是动物，总有一天有人会发脾气。那部电影里有一声尖叫，当我告诉你我为那声尖叫奋斗了三个月时，我不是在开玩笑。对于乔治来说，这是一场漫长的比赛。” </p><figure id="attachment_3603611" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603611" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603611" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy.jpg" alt="《福瑞奥莎：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/furiosa_anya_taylorjoy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3603611" class="wp-caption-text"> 《福瑞奥莎：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》。图片来源：华纳兄弟影业</figcaption></figure><p><em>《福瑞奥莎：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》</em>将于 3 月 23 日上映，已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/furiosa-is-a-ferocious-prequel-to-mad-max-fury-road-say-critics-3754034">获得看过这部动作大片的影评人的好评</a>。 <a href="https://twitter.com/ErikDavis/status/1787656513789530128" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Fandango</em>的埃里克·戴维斯 (Erik Davis)</a>将这部电影描述为“一部凶猛且节奏紧凑的史诗，扩展了<em>福瑞奥萨</em>和荒原的故事，同时呈现了最疯狂的追逐、最夸张的角色和令人惊叹的摄影。”</p><p>这部电影由安雅·泰勒-乔伊和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-hemsworth">克里斯·海姆斯沃斯</a>主演，将作为 2015 年汤姆·哈迪、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charlize-theron">查理兹·塞隆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zo-kravitz">佐伊·克拉维茨</a>主演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/best-film-past-25-years-rotten-tomatoes-3473276"><em>《疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路》</em></a>的前传。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/furiosa-is-a-ferocious-prequel-to-mad-max-fury-road-say-critics-3754034"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>另据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/furiosa-has-an-action-scene-that-took-78-days-to-film-3749217">上个月有消息称，</a> <em>《Furiosa》</em>中的一场动作戏拍摄耗时 78 天。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anya-taylor-joy-only-has-30-lines-of-dialogue-in-furiosa-went-months-without-speaking-on-set-3755963">安雅·泰勒-乔伊 (Anya Taylor-Joy) 在《Furiosa》中只有 30 句台词，“几个月”没有在片场讲话的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
