 Serj Tankian 透露 System Of A Down 在 2018 年主动提出退出乐队后试镜了一位新歌手https://www.nme.com/news/music/serj-tankian-reveals-system-of-a-down-auditioned-a-new-singer-in-2018-after-he-offered-to-quit- the-band-3755943?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=serj-tankian-揭示了 2018 年新歌手在他提出退出后的试镜系统乐队Surej SinghTue, 14 May 2024 07:21:36 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3755943 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>坦基安告诉乐队他不想再巡演并且不会阻止他们之后</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/serj-tankian-reveals-system-of-a-down-auditioned-a-new-singer-in-2018-after-he-offered-to-quit-the-band-3755943">Serj Tankian 透露 System Of A Down 于 2018 年试镜了一位新歌手，此前他提出退出乐队，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Serj-Tankian-performing-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/serj-tankian">Serj Tankian</a>透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/system-of-a-down">System Of A Down</a>在提出退出乐队后于 2018 年开始寻找新歌手。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/serj-tankian-interview-elasticity-system-of-a-down-2915097-2915097">塞尔吉·坦基安（Serj Tankian）：“我认为特朗普的下台让全世界都松了口气”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在他与<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/serj-tankian-down-with-the-system-a-memoir-book-excerpt-1235018834/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>分享的新回忆录<em>《Down With the System: A Memoir (Of Sorts)》</em>中，坦基安反思了他对巡演的蔑视，导致他决定告诉 System Of A Down 中的乐队成员在没有他的情况下继续进行下去。他们可以继续实现他们的梦想。</p><p> Tankian 在回忆录中详细介绍道：“2017 年底，我们在 [乐队经理] Beno 的办公室举行了一次乐队会议。当我到达时，我告诉大家我有一个项目想添加到议程中。我们进行了繁琐的常规业务讨论，然后就到了我的项目的时候了。”</p><p> “那么，谁将为我举办一场告别派对呢？”我问了群里的人。 “你们中有人想成为司仪吗？”我笑了一点，但我很认真。 “听着，伙计们，我已经很清楚地表明，我不再对巡演感兴趣，因为我的背部和这不再是我的视野范围内的事情。” </p><figure id="attachment_3751975" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3751975" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3751975" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/serj-tankian@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/serj-tankian@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/serj-tankian@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/serj-tankian@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/serj-tankian@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/serj-tankian@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/serj-tankian@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3751975" class="wp-caption-text">塞尔吉·坦基安.图片来源：丹尼尔·奈顿/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>“‘但问题是，’我继续说道，‘我不想阻止你们。这是你的梦想。这就是你一生的努力。你值得拥有这个。我看着达伦、沙沃和约翰，知道我接下来说的话会造成沉重打击。 “我认为你们应该找一位新歌手。”</p><p>他继续说道，后来补充说乐队反对这个想法，他们完全放弃了这个话题。然而，一段时间后，乐队聚集在一次慈善活动上，坦基安被告知乐队已经开始寻找新歌手。</p><p> “我有点以为他们已经忘记了雇用一位新歌手的整个想法，但大约一年后，约翰、沙沃和我参加了格伦代尔的一场筹款活动，我认识的这位歌手站起来唱了一首优美的歌曲。亚美尼亚歌曲。沙沃坐在我旁边的桌子上。他俯身拍拍我的肩膀。”</p><p> “‘顺便说一句，’他向歌手点点头，‘我们尝试过这个人当歌手。唯一的问题是他无法尖叫和咆哮。”我吃了一惊。并不是说他们一直在试镜替代者，而是他们保守了这个秘密。” </p><figure id="attachment_3077061" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3077061" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3077061" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/serj-tankian-system-of-a-down-getty-kevin-winter.jpg" alt="洛杉矶的 Serj Tankian 系统推迟了 covid-19" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/serj-tankian-system-of-a-down-getty-kevin-winter.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/serj-tankian-system-of-a-down-getty-kevin-winter-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/serj-tankian-system-of-a-down-getty-kevin-winter-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/serj-tankian-system-of-a-down-getty-kevin-winter-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/serj-tankian-system-of-a-down-getty-kevin-winter-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/serj-tankian-system-of-a-down-getty-kevin-winter-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3077061" class="wp-caption-text"> System Of A Down 的 Serj Tankian。图片来源：凯文·温特/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>坦基安继续写道：“‘你们为什么不告诉我？’我低声说道。沙沃耸耸肩。 &#39;我不知道。&#39;我转向沙沃，现在直视着他。 “听着，他是个好歌手，”我说。 “我现在就可以带他去停车场，教他如何咆哮。你真的应该考虑一下他。”</p><p> Serj Tankian 还表示，“最近几年”，他曾推荐一位亲密的朋友作为潜在的替代者，但他认为乐队从未认真考虑过这一提议。</p><p>目前看来，乐队对让 Tankian 加入乐队的决定立场坚定，并大幅减少了现场演出的数量。该乐队在 2023 年只演出了一场演出，今年迄今为止也只演出了一场。接下来，他们将在八月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deftones-and-system-of-a-down-announce-huge-headline-show-with-the-mars-volta-and-more-3615554">与 Deftones、The Mars Volta 等乐队一起演出一场一次性演出</a>。该剧现已售罄。 </p><figure id="attachment_3754998" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3754998" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3754998" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Serj-Tankain-performing.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Serj-Tankain-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Serj-Tankain-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Serj-Tankain-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Serj-Tankain-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Serj-Tankain-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Serj-Tankain-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3754998" class="wp-caption-text"> System of a Down 乐队主唱 Serj Tankian 在佛罗伦萨摇滚音乐节的音乐会上。意大利佛罗伦萨。 2017 年 6 月 25 日（摄影：Francesco Castaldo/Archivio Francesco Castaldo/Mondadori via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>早在 2020 年，System Of A Down 就带着 15 年来的首张新专辑回归——双 A 面单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/system-of-a-down-share-first-new-songs-in-15-years-protect-the-land-and-genocidal-humanoidz-2810433">《Protect The Land》和《Genocidal Humanoidz》</a> ——旨在提高人们对“一场可怕而严重的战争”的认识并筹集资金。 ”阿尔扎赫和阿塞拜疆之间。所有收益均用于支持 SOAD 祖籍亚美尼亚的人道主义工作。</p><p>其他消息方面，Tankian <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/system-of-a-downs-serj-tankian-announces-solo-ep-teases-heavy-new-single-a-f-day-3751974">最近宣布了一张新的个人 EP《Foundations》</a> ，这将是他自 2022 年发行个人 EP《Perplex Cities》以来的第一个项目。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/serj-tankian-reveals-system-of-a-down-auditioned-a-new-singer-in-2018-after-he-offered-to-quit-the-band-3755943">Serj Tankian 透露 System Of A Down 于 2018 年试镜了一位新歌手，此前他提出退出乐队，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Aminé 将于今年八月在波特兰推出新节日“The Best Day Ever” https://www.nme.com/news/music/amine-to-launch-new-festival-the-best-day-ever-in-portland-this-august-3755929?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=amine-今年八月将推出波特兰有史以来最好的一天新节日Surej SinghTue, 14 May 2024 06:33:46 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsRaphttps://www.nme.com/?p=3755929 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Kaytranada、BADBADNOTGOOD、Toro y Moi 等将在为期两天的首届活动中表演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/amine-to-launch-new-festival-the-best-day-ever-in-portland-this-august-3755929">Aminé 将于今年八月在波特兰推出新音乐节“The Best Day Ever in Portland”</a>的帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/amine-kaytranada@2000x1270-696x442.jp